room_title: Escape room "Outlaw: Jailbreak" by What The Lock? in Manitowoc
room_description: It is 1884 and you and your gang have been rounded up and jailed by the Sheriff for a local bank heist. In the morning the hangman is arriving by train to carry out your sentence. Fortunately for you, the Sheriff just left for dinner... You have one hour to escape the cell, locate your loot and escape before the sheriff returns.
